Verdad licensing
================

Except where a file, directory, or embedded notice says otherwise, the
Verdad-authored source code in this repository is available under either of
the following licenses, at your option:

- GNU General Public License, version 2 only
- The Unlicense

The full license texts are included in:

- `LICENSES/GPL-2.0-only.txt`
- `LICENSES/Unlicense.txt`

This dual-license notice applies to Verdad-authored code only. It does not
relicense bundled third-party code such as `libs/litehtml/`, nor any file that
already carries its own separate licensing notice.

Third-party license texts and notices relevant to Verdad are bundled under
`LICENSES/`.

Distribution note
-----------------

Verdad links against CrossWire SWORD. SWORD is licensed under GPL version 2, so
distributed builds of Verdad that link against SWORD need to comply with the
GPL-2.0 obligations that arise from that combined distribution.
